{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"28da93c49b","title":"致各中央局、分局电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"57e3c44b3d","index":0,"year":1946,"month":7,"day":10,"articleId":"28da93c49b"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji21","name":"毛泽东全集第21卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji21.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji21":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"fc680aad28","type":"paragraph","text":"致各中央局、分局电","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"28da93c49b"},{"id":"bb0fe50f35","type":"paragraph","text":"（1946年7月10日）必须认识介石此种作法的两面性：一方面，国际国内大局道使他不能全国大打，有些地方兵力不够也无法大打，故申言要停战，要和平，我党力量强大及坚决斗争是道便他如此做的最主要因素：另方面，对五师，对胶济，已在大打，对苏皖即将大打，对豫北对热河亦在准备打，均以自卫为名。此种边打边谈以打为主的局面，至少还将继续一时期，各地应充分注意粉碎落介石的进攻[1]这是毛泽东关于通报马歌尔转来蒋介石发给全国各长官的一个以白","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"28da93c49b"}],"page":{"id":"aa4c0cf38b","publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"28da93c49b","start":477,"end":477}}}},"__N_SSG":true}